You can generate doxygen documentation for the API from here.
1. Go in the doxygen directory
2. do "doxygen doxygen.cfg"

By default, it will generate the documentation in the html and latex format.
-> Just type "firefox html/index" to get access to the local page
of the generated documentation.

The whole doxygen documentation generation can be configure in the doxygen.cfg file
Please refere to the Doxygen documentation for more details.

link: http://www.stack.nl/~dimitri/doxygen/

